NOTES for GPU compilation
1. Recompile cuda code on each cuda machine, nvcc compiler does the optimization for you
2. gProf may have difficulty with profiling c code, use the CUDA profiler.
3. to compile with cuBLAS - nvcc -c cudaSample.cu -o example -lcublas
4. dynamic values passed to a cuda kernel must be in gpu shared memory
5. nvcc -arch=compute_13 or nvcc -arch=compute_11
6. nvcc cuTriad.cu -IC:\Users\leont\cuda-samples\Common - for lenovo
7. similar to 6 for the dell
